snippet: Michigan Coach John Beilein got the better of his son Patrick when the 25th-ranked Wolverines beat Le Moyne, 74-52, in an exhibition game in Ann Arbor.
abstract: University of Michigan Coach John Beilein leads men's basketball team to victory over Le Moyne College, which is coached by his son Patrick, 74-52, in exhibition game.
lead_paragraph: Michigan Coach John Beilein got the better of his son Patrick when the 25th-ranked Wolverines beat Le Moyne, 74-52, in an exhibition game in Ann Arbor.
